        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/df705f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2016-12-04T02:42:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Also one more question for clarification - when you say three hour double decant, do you mean you let it sit in decanter for three hours before pouring back into the magnum, or do you decant, clean, the bottle, pour back into bottle, and then wait three hours?</p>\n<p>Tx.</p>",
