        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/arv_r/{size}/76949_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-12-04T04:17:26.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had some strong metallic notes on some 1970 Magdelaine\u2019s.  Others who were familiar with the estate didn\u2019t pick them up, or it didn\u2019t bother them as we drank, but it was always weird to me.  I thought there was a flaw, or damage.</p>",
